<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Informix cut.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Informix cut.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Smith Barney confirmed it downgraded Informix Corp to &quot;outperform high risk&quot; from &quot;buy high risk.&quot;</p>
<p>-- said cut the 1997 earnings estimate to $0.82 a share from $0.90 a share. Trimmed the 1998 estimate to $1.25 a share from $1.30.</p>
<p>-- said likes the stock long-term, but said Informix will will not see renewed earnings per share growth until the second half of 1997.</p>
<p>-- expects the company's operating expenses in the first half of the year will be higher than expected.</p>
</text>
